    <string name="add_server_guide_close">Close</string>
    <string name="add_server_guide_message">1. Download and extract the ServerAgent package.\n\n2. Open terminal in the extracted folder.\n\n3. Run first-time setup:\npython3 setup.py\n\n4. Setup will register server and show pairing code + QR.\n\n5. In app, scan QR (or type code) and tap PAIR SERVER.\n\n6. After successful pairing, setup creates and enables the systemd service automatically.</string>

